India Finance Ministry to Meet This Week on State Bank Infusion

-- B y   A n t o   A n t o n y
-- 
2011-10-18T13:06:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/india-finance-ministry-to-meet-this-week-on-state-bank-infusion.html
India ’s finance ministry will meet
this week to decide on infusing capital into  State Bank of
India (SBIN) , D.K. Mittal, the country’s banking secretary, said in New
Delhi today.  The government may consider buying preference shares in the
lender, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
